videos.headline: Chance Allen outjumps defender for TD
videos.description: Houston's Chance Allen gets the better of UConn's Jhavon Williams for the 38-yard touchdown to bring Houston to within 13-10.

videos.headline: Tricky, tricky Huskies score on double-pass TD
videos.description: UConn quarterback Tim Boyle's backwards pass is almost intercepted, but gets to Garrett Anderson who heaves it down field to Noel Thomas for the catch and score to put the underdog Huskies up 20-10.

videos.headline: Wilson goes 94-yards in a flash for TD
videos.description: Houston's Brandon Wilson takes the kickoff and puts on the jets, going 94 yards for the touchdown to cut the Cougars' deficit to 20-17.

videos.headline: UConn seals upset with interception
videos.description: With Houston driving for the winning score, UConn's Jamar Summers picks off Greg Ward Jr. to knock the Cougars from the ranks of the unbeatens.
